properties.name: com.jasonpyau.app-password
properties.description: Admin Panel password used for the Admin Panel CLI and Spring Boot server to authenticate.

properties.name: com.jasonpyau.email
properties.description: Used to send email notifications after someone sends a message via the 'Contact Me' section.

properties.name: com.jasonpyau.rate-limit.tokens-per-interval
properties.description: Number of tokens allowed to be used per interval per user for RateLimitService.java. Default value: 600

properties.name: com.jasonpyau.rate-limit.interval-duration
properties.description: Number of seconds a user has to wait until their tokens are fully reset for RateLimitService.java. Default value: 30

properties.name: com.jasonpyau.cache.clear-rate
properties.description: How often, in minutes, to clear/clean caches for Experiences, Skills, Projects, Rate Limit, etc. Default value: 240
